</div>
<hr>
<!-- Information about the club holiday using div containers and hero-units -->
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <h2>Club Holiday 2012-13</h2>

        Oval Ski Club organise a holiday to one of the popular skiing resorts in Europe every year. The holiday is usually arranged over the Easter break making it available for all club members to come along. The group size varies each year and this is based on flight availability and what the demand levels  are expected to be. This can be anything from 50 - 100 people.<br>
        <br>

        <p>Details of this seasons holiday are shown below:</p>

        This seasons holiday will be held in either St.Christoph or St.Anton in Austria. The holiday date that has been arranged is Saturday 23rd March - 30th March 2013.<br>
        <br>
        
        Feel free to click on the links provided below to view or request a holiday brochure for the holiday destinations mentioned above:<br>
        <br>
        <!-- a href links to holiday brochures -->
        <p><a href="http://www.espritski.com/about/brochure/">St.Anton 1</a></p>
        <p><a href="http://www.markwarner.co.uk/brochure-request">St.Anton 2</a></p>
        <p><a href="http://www.elegantresorts.co.uk/members/e-brochures">St.Christoph 1</a></p>
        <p><a href="http://www.inghams.co.uk/my-inghams/brochure-requests/">St.Christoph 2</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-unit">
        <h3>Further Information</h3>

        For further details about this years club holiday or to book a place, please speak to Andy Kearney. He's usually at most of the club sessions on both Saturday and Sunday. He can be contacted on 07855662891.
      </div>
      <hr>

      <footer>
      <!-- Links to Facebook and Twitter -->
